        "description": {
          "zh-cn": "日本于1945年8月15日宣布无条件投降，并于9月2日正式签署降伏文书，结束了太平洋战争。",
          "en": "Japan announced its unconditional surrender on August 15, 1945, and formally signed the Instrument of Surrender on September 2, ending the Pacific War."
        }
      }
    },
