        "end_date": "1945-08-09",
        "description": {
          "zh-cn": "美国对广岛和长崎投下原子弹，对日本政府造成巨大冲击，是促使其决定投降的关键因素之一。",
          "en": "The atomic bombings of Hiroshima and Nagasaki by the United States shocked the Japanese government and were one of the key factors that pushed it to decide to surrender."
        }
      }
    },
